    <div class="">
        <div class="page-title">
            <div class="title_left">
                <h3>User Profile</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="title_right">
                <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 form-group pull-right top_search">
                    <input class="btn btn-dark" type="button" value="Publicar" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" />
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>

        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                <div class="x_panel">
                    <div class="x_title">
                        <h2>User Report <small>Activity report</small></h2>
                   
                        <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="x_content">
                        <div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1 col-xs-12 profile_left">
                    
                          
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-10 col-xs-12">
                            <div class="profile_title form-group">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <h2>Publicaciones</h2>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-4">

                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-2">
                                @*<input class="btn btn-dark" type="button" value="Publicar" />*@
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-lg-12">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                                            <h4><strong><a href="#">Title of the post</a></strong></h4>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-lg-4 "  >
                                            <a class="thumbnail">
                                                <img src="http://placehold.it/260x180" alt="" width="260" height="180">
                                            </a>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-lg-8">
                                            <p>
                                                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, id nec conceptam conclusionemque. Et eam tation option. Utinam salutatus ex eum. Ne mea dicit tibique facilisi, ea mei omittam explicari conclusionemque, ad nobis propriae quaerendum sea.
                                            </p>
                                            <p><a class="btn btn-dark" href="#">Read more</a></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-lg-12">
                                            <p></p>
                                            <p>
                                                <span class="fa fa-user"></span> by <a href="#">John</a>
                                                | <i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> Sept 16th, 2012
